thread.title: Richard SWAN

author: Richard SWAN
title: Richard SWAN
text:
Prompt efficient service + an great leather wallet cover for my Samsung S6.
I was always kept up to date with the progress of my order. I received my wallet after 3 days, great service.
I have recommended your Company to my friend Mr Bryan Randall and he has purchased a wallet as well. I shall be definitely shopping again on your very comprehensive website shop.
Many thanks again
regards
Richard Swan
